thread.title: Judith
thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by Judith

author: Judith
title: Judith
text: The mat and plexi were beautifully cut. The frame was of high quality, but the corners weren't quite as tight as I like. I ended up filling two of the corners with glue and pin nailing with my nail gun to pull them together, then I had to fill the nail holes. I would have reordered, but I needed the frame right away and didn't have time to send it back.
